Gastrointestinal: Abdominal pain, pseudomembranous colitis, esophagitis, nausea, vomiting and diarrhea (see 
   BOXED WARNING
). The onset of pseudomembranous colitis symptoms may occur during or after antibacterial treatment (see 
   WARNINGS
). An unpleasant or metallic taste has been reported after oral administration.
